ScamShield: Your scam-fighting sidekick

ScamShield helps protect you from scams by blocking shady calls, filtering scammy SMSes, and letting you check suspicious messages before clicking anything regrettable.

Here’s what ScamShield can do:

[New] Get notified when a number you reported gets flagged
- If the authorities later mark a number you reported as possibly used by scammers, we’ll send you a push notification. You can also check your history of flagged numbers in the app.

Spot a scam before it gets you
- Got a weird link, message, or phone number? Paste it in to see if it might be a scam. You can even upload screenshots - works for SMS, WhatsApp, and Telegram too.

Block and filter scam calls & SMSes
- Follow our quick setup guide to block known scam numbers and filter out sketchy messages.

Report suspicious calls, messages, and links
- Help the community by reporting scams - with screenshots if you have them. The more we know, the better we can protect everyone.

Heads up: Submitting a scam report in the app isn't the same as filing an official police report. If you've been scammed, please file an e-report with the Singapore Police Force.

Download ScamShield for yourself and your loved ones because a little protection goes a long way.

Feedback? Ideas? Love letters?
Tell us at go.gov.sg/scamshield-share-feedback

ScamShield is built by Open Government Products, in collaboration with the Singapore Police Force (SPF) and the National Crime Prevention Council (NCPC).

Postal Vote BD is the official mobile application developed by the Bangladesh Election Commission to enroll voters and track ballot papers only at home and abroad. However, voters will exercise their voting by manually casting vote in a postal ballot paper sent by postal services. Voters will send this ballot paper by postal service to concerned electoral official(s) in Bangladesh. This secure and verified platform enables eligible voters to exercise their democratic rights conveniently from anywhere.

CURRENT FEATURES:

- Enrollment & Registration
Start enrollment directly from the app. Simply provide registered mobile number to create a secure profile.

- Voter Enrollment:
Complete verification through a secure eKYC process, followed by a facial verification with liveness detection to confirm voter identity. User can also provide passport details (optional) and postal address for receive postal ballot.

- Ballot Tracking:
Once voters are registered and verified, a ballot is prepared and sent to your registered postal address(obtained during enrolment process). Voter can track the delivery status of ballot within the app to ensure safe and timely arrival.

- Ballot Return and Verification:
After receiving a ballot, simply scan the QR code printed on the enve using the app. Complete a quick liveness check, cast a vote on the paper ballot, and return the envelope to voter designated constituency for official processing.

- Notifications & Reminders
Receive timely alerts about deadlines, application status, and important updates.

- Multi-language Support
Available in both Bangla and English for convenience of voters.

- Notifications & Reminders
Receive timely alerts about deadlines, application status, and important updates.

- Multi-language Support
Available in both Bangla and English for convenience of voters.

PREREQUISITE:
- A registered mobile number
- A valid National ID (NID) card
- A valid passport
- A valid postal address

WHO CAN USE THIS APP:

- Bangladeshi elligible voters living abroad
- Government officials on duty
- Members of law enforcing agencies
- Electoral officials
- Other eligible voters as per Bangaldesh Election Commission guidelines

SECURITY & PRIVACY:

Data security is the top most priority. Postal Vote BD mobile application follows strict government data protection protocols. All personal information is securely stored and processed in accordance with Bangladesh's data protection regulations.

OFFICIAL & VERIFIED:

This is the only official postal voting app authorized by the Bangladesh Election Commission. Beware of fraudulent applications.

SUPPORT:

For assistance, please contact:
Email: info@ocv.gov.bd
Contact:

Google Authenticator adds an extra layer of security to your online accounts by adding a second step of verification when you sign in. This means that in addition to your password, you'll also need to enter a code that is generated by the Google Authenticator app on your phone.

The verification code can be generated by the Google Authenticator app on your phone, even if you don't have a network or mobile connection.

• Sync your Authenticator codes to your Google Account and across your devices. This way, you can always access them even if you lose your phone.

• Set up your Authenticator accounts automatically with a QR code. This is quick and easy, and it helps to ensure that your codes are set up correctly.

• Support for multiple accounts. You can use the authenticator app to manage multiple accounts, so you don't have to switch between apps every time you need to sign in.

• Support for time-based and counter-based code generation. You can choose the type of code generation that best suits your needs.

• Transfer accounts between devices with a QR code. This is a convenient way to move your accounts to a new device.


To use Google Authenticator with Google, you need to enable 2-Step Verification on your Google Account. To get started, visit http://www.google.com/2step
